      "content": "Hello, Koryn. Welcome to the realm of Eldrath, where ancient magic hums beneath the surface and the echoes of forgotten wars linger in the wind. You stand at the edge of a village called Virelle, nestled between the mist-shrouded peaks of the Frostspire Mountains and the winding River Thalor. The air is crisp with the scent of pine and damp earth, and the distant sound of a bell tolls from the village square, marking the hour of dawn.\n\nBefore you lies a cobbled path that winds through the village, leading toward the inn where you’ve been told to meet your companions. But as you step forward, the wind shifts, carrying with it the faint scent of charred wood and something… metallic. A low murmur rises from the streets—whispers of a strange occurrence last night, of a fire that burned without flame, and of a shadow that moved where no one was.\n\nWhat will you do, Koryn?",
